## Use cases

- To provide the user with a means of leaving the current context.
- With long pages that have clear ways of sectioning the content.
- As a companion to a Primary Button to return the previous context.

## Limitations

- For actions requiring submission or manipulation of data,
consider using <a href="button.html">buttons</a>.

